1
00:00:00,410 --> 00:00:01,670
Once Seo Rin wakes up,

2
00:00:02,510 --> 00:00:03,810
get rid of Oh Jang Mi.

3
00:00:04,280 --> 00:00:08,810
- Understood.
- In any case, we don't need the twins.

4
00:00:09,280 --> 00:00:10,280
Absolutely not.

5
00:00:10,680 --> 00:00:12,850
That's how it was back then,
and that's how it is now.

6
00:00:14,350 --> 00:00:16,650
One of them has to die.

7
00:00:17,960 --> 00:00:19,790
One of us has to die?

8
00:00:20,590 --> 00:00:24,760
Does that mean she tried
to kill Oh Jang Mi with that truck?

9
00:01:29,860 --> 00:01:31,960
It's so good to hear your voice.

10
00:01:33,570 --> 00:01:34,930
Have you eaten?

11
00:01:36,670 --> 00:01:37,670
What did you have?

12
00:01:40,870 --> 00:01:43,040
Really? Sounds delicious.

13
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:45,040
Anything new with you?

14
00:01:47,250 --> 00:01:48,250
Honey.

15
00:01:49,350 --> 00:01:51,020
You know. Same old, same old.

16
00:01:51,380 --> 00:01:53,150
I'm bored to death, seriously.

17
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:56,960
What? You're coming to visit tomorrow?

18
00:01:57,660 --> 00:01:59,520
Of course I'd love that.

19
00:01:59,520 --> 00:02:00,560
All right, then.

20
00:02:10,340 --> 00:02:12,370
In any case,

21
00:02:12,370 --> 00:02:13,970
we don't need the twins.

22
00:02:14,610 --> 00:02:15,910
Absolutely not.

23
00:02:15,910 --> 00:02:18,140
That's how it was back then,
and that's how it is now.

24
00:02:34,860 --> 00:02:38,400
Oh Jang Mi is acting like
she has nine lives.

25
00:02:39,100 --> 00:02:40,370
Once Seo Rin wakes up,

26
00:02:41,030 --> 00:02:42,300
get rid of Oh Jang Mi.

27
00:02:43,770 --> 00:02:44,770
Oh Jang Mi.

28
00:02:45,540 --> 00:02:46,870
Oh Jang Mi.

29
00:02:46,870 --> 00:02:47,940
Jang Mi.

30
00:02:50,380 --> 00:02:51,440
Seo Rin.

31
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:54,150
Ma Seo Rin.

32
00:04:07,050 --> 00:04:08,820
Seo Rin, did you have a good dream?

33
00:04:09,650 --> 00:04:11,020
It's your wedding day today.

34
00:04:11,590 --> 00:04:13,490
You need a big breakfast
to get through it.

35
00:04:14,060 --> 00:04:15,390
Yes, Grandpa.

36
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:19,460
This is the last time...

37
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:21,730
we'll all have breakfast together,
just our family.

38
00:04:22,430 --> 00:04:25,470
Grandpa, I'm not going anywhere
just because I'm getting married.

39
00:04:27,670 --> 00:04:28,740
My sweet girl.

40
00:04:29,540 --> 00:04:32,910
But still, I can't help
but feel a little empty,

41
00:04:33,210 --> 00:04:34,780
and so proud at the same time.

42
00:04:35,110 --> 00:04:37,650
She'll have a happy marriage, Father,
so please don't worry.

43
00:04:38,250 --> 00:04:41,850
- Jun Ho will love and cherish her.
- Of course. Absolutely.

44
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:43,190
Don't you worry.

45
00:04:54,770 --> 00:04:56,600
So, it's Jang Mi's wedding today.

46
00:04:57,670 --> 00:04:58,670
Just like this...

47
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:00,710
Should I really let it end like this?

48
00:05:03,780 --> 00:05:04,940
It's not too late.

49
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:06,640
Please.

50
00:05:11,250 --> 00:05:12,820
(Baek Ho)

51
00:05:17,290 --> 00:05:18,460
Baek Ho.

52
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:20,960
No.

53
00:05:21,590 --> 00:05:22,690
Please, don't.

54
00:05:27,700 --> 00:05:30,000
The person you are calling is unavailable.

55
00:05:41,450 --> 00:05:42,450
Yes, sir?

56
00:05:43,980 --> 00:05:44,980
Sorry, what was that?

57
00:05:45,980 --> 00:05:48,650
You restored the GPS data
and found the address?

58
00:05:49,790 --> 00:05:51,260
Thank you.

59
00:05:51,260 --> 00:05:52,290
Thank you so much.

60
00:05:53,260 --> 00:05:55,160
- Congratulations.
- Congratulations.

61
00:05:55,230 --> 00:05:56,230
Welcome.

62
00:05:56,960 --> 00:05:57,960
Congratulations.

63
00:05:58,900 --> 00:05:59,900
Congratulations.

64
00:06:01,300 --> 00:06:02,500
- This is our daughter.
- You're all grown up!

65
00:06:02,570 --> 00:06:03,940
- She's all grown up.
- You'll be next to get married!

66
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:06,270
- She's getting married next month.
- My goodness, really?

67
00:06:06,340 --> 00:06:07,970
- Congratulations.
- Thank you. Please join the reception.

68
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:09,270
- We will.
- We'll see you again later.

69
00:06:09,340 --> 00:06:10,810
Yes, thank you.

70
00:06:26,290 --> 00:06:28,630
Don't you look lovely,
Mother of the Bride.

71
00:06:29,860 --> 00:06:30,860
Congratulations.

72
00:06:31,230 --> 00:06:35,000
- You could pass for the bride, CEO Chae.
- And what in the world are you wearing?

73
00:06:35,230 --> 00:06:37,100
I guess you think
you're the star of the day.

74
00:06:37,540 --> 00:06:39,970
You're going to sweep the floor
with that dress.

75
00:06:42,870 --> 00:06:43,880
Father, you're here.

76
00:06:45,140 --> 00:06:46,240
Go on, take him to his seat.

77
00:06:46,540 --> 00:06:49,380
- Congratulations, ma'am.
- Go check on the bridal suite.

78
00:06:49,650 --> 00:06:51,150
Seo Rin must be getting lonely in there.

79
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,480
Okay.

80
00:06:53,180 --> 00:06:57,560
- I guess Lawyer Kang isn't here yet?
- What?

81
00:06:57,960 --> 00:06:59,090
Hey, listen.

82
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:01,860
If Lawyer Kang isn't here yet,

83
00:07:02,060 --> 00:07:05,300
have him go to my house
and get a bag for me.

84
00:07:05,460 --> 00:07:08,430
I prepared some spending money
for Seo Rin's honeymoon,

85
00:07:09,130 --> 00:07:11,640
- but I completely forgot to bring it.
- Yes, sir.

86
00:07:16,940 --> 00:07:18,110
Yes, honey.

87
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:20,310
You're there already?

88
00:07:20,810 --> 00:07:23,710
You know that cafe near the intersection?
Go wait for me there.

89
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:25,080
I'll be right there.

90
00:08:14,170 --> 00:08:16,570
- Can I help you?
- I'm here looking for someone.

91
00:08:16,630 --> 00:08:18,700
Who? This is a restricted area.

92
00:08:19,270 --> 00:08:22,410
Restricted?
Do you have any idea who you're stopping?

93
00:08:22,740 --> 00:08:24,110
And who are you?

94
00:08:27,310 --> 00:08:28,310
Is this enough?

95
00:08:29,250 --> 00:08:32,250
I'm investigating a report that a woman
is being held captive here. Move.

96
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:38,290
- Hey, stop right there!
- Get him!

97
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:47,600
Taxi!

98
00:09:22,330 --> 00:09:23,940
We're finally getting married.

99
00:09:24,470 --> 00:09:27,140
I know.
After everything we've been through,

100
00:09:27,740 --> 00:09:28,740
we finally made it.

101
00:09:35,950 --> 00:09:36,950
You look so beautiful.

102
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:40,220
More beautiful than words can say.

103
00:09:48,730 --> 00:09:50,760
Wait here, please.
I'll be right back with the fare.

104
00:10:03,070 --> 00:10:04,080
Grandpa!

105
00:10:04,980 --> 00:10:05,980
Mom!

106
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:09,280
What's going on?

107
00:10:09,910 --> 00:10:11,080
Where is everyone?

108
00:10:11,850 --> 00:10:13,650
Why is the house so empty?

109
00:10:15,990 --> 00:10:17,590
(You are invited to the wedding
of Kang Jun Ho and Ma Seo Rin)

110
00:10:23,930 --> 00:10:24,930
Kang Jun Ho?

111
00:10:26,700 --> 00:10:28,800
Ma Seo Rin and Kang Jun Ho
are getting married?

112
00:10:29,800 --> 00:10:32,370
But I'm Ma Seo Rin right here.

113
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:34,440
Then who am I supposed to be marrying?

114
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:39,740
Has Oh Jang Mi been impersonating me
this whole time?

115
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:41,310
In my own home,

116
00:10:41,580 --> 00:10:44,580
living under my name,
and now she's even marrying my fiance?

117
00:10:44,820 --> 00:10:45,820
Shit!

118
00:10:46,350 --> 00:10:47,450
This can't be happening!

119
00:10:50,150 --> 00:10:51,260
Oh Jang Mi.

120
00:10:51,820 --> 00:10:53,520
It was Oh Jang Mi
getting married all along.

121
00:10:53,820 --> 00:10:55,030
To my beloved Jun Ho!

122
00:10:55,830 --> 00:10:56,830
Oh Jang Mi.

123
00:10:57,290 --> 00:10:59,660
I escaped and came all this way
to save you.

124
00:11:00,060 --> 00:11:02,230
How could you betray me like this?

125
00:11:02,230 --> 00:11:03,400
How could you?

126
00:11:07,670 --> 00:11:08,670
Hong Ju.

127
00:11:09,270 --> 00:11:12,040
The ceremony hasn't started yet, has it?

128
00:11:12,280 --> 00:11:14,480
Mom, where have you been?
I couldn't find you anywhere.

129
00:11:14,610 --> 00:11:18,680
You won't believe it, but I forgot to wear
my important diamond ring.

130
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:23,290
I have to wear it in the family photo
to stake my claim as the Chairman's wife.

131
00:11:23,450 --> 00:11:27,060
- Hurry. The ceremony's about to start.
- All right, you brat.

132
00:11:28,860 --> 00:11:30,230
Oh my gosh, you scared me!

133
00:11:33,630 --> 00:11:34,630
Who are you?

134
00:11:38,270 --> 00:11:40,670
Seo Rin?

135
00:11:41,870 --> 00:11:45,340
No, that can't be.
Seo Rin is at her wedding right now.

136
00:11:45,810 --> 00:11:46,980
Then, are you Oh Jang Mi?

137
00:11:46,980 --> 00:11:49,610
You're Oh Jang Mi, aren't you?

138
00:11:49,610 --> 00:11:51,020
Then what are you doing here?

139
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:53,550
Are you crazy?
Who are you calling Oh Jang Mi?

140
00:11:53,650 --> 00:11:58,220
Shit, I'm right here!
Who said they could get married?

141
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:03,060
I'm not letting them get away with this.

142
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:10,800
What in the world...

143
00:12:11,340 --> 00:12:13,600
What is she talking about?

144
00:12:17,640 --> 00:12:18,640
What is this?

145
00:12:19,340 --> 00:12:21,650
Don't tell me Oh Jang Mi
took over my room, too.

146
00:12:24,220 --> 00:12:25,320
Oh Jang Mi.

147
00:12:25,980 --> 00:12:27,690
As if impersonating me wasn't bad enough,

148
00:12:28,150 --> 00:12:30,320
you had to take over my room
and even my man?

149
00:12:30,890 --> 00:12:31,990
Shit.

150
00:12:32,920 --> 00:12:34,290
I'll make her pay for this.

151
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:47,340
So my phone was here the whole time.

152
00:12:56,680 --> 00:12:57,680
Ma Seo Rin?

153
00:12:59,680 --> 00:13:00,680
Ma Seo Rin.

154
00:13:01,890 --> 00:13:03,590
Seo Rin.

155
00:13:04,390 --> 00:13:06,260
To the Dream Hotel, and step on it.

156
00:13:06,460 --> 00:13:08,130
- Quickly!
- Ma Seo Rin, I need to talk to you.

157
00:13:08,290 --> 00:13:10,160
Ma Seo Rin!

158
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:34,050
(Groom: Kang Jun Ho, Bride: Ma Seo Rin)

159
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:40,120
Oh Jang Mi.

160
00:13:40,930 --> 00:13:42,430
How could you?

161
00:13:43,530 --> 00:13:44,900
How dare you steal my man from me?

162
00:13:45,460 --> 00:13:47,400
How could you do this to me?

163
00:13:56,810 --> 00:13:57,810
Tae Pyung.

164
00:13:58,940 --> 00:14:00,110
You look so beautiful, Jang Mi.

165
00:14:00,910 --> 00:14:03,450
But are you sure you won't regret this?

166
00:14:04,750 --> 00:14:06,350
There's no turning back now.

167
00:14:06,950 --> 00:14:08,020
Think this through.

168
00:14:11,490 --> 00:14:13,660
I've thought about this a million times.

169
00:14:14,160 --> 00:14:15,560
Dad would've loved...

170
00:14:16,860 --> 00:14:18,630
to see you in your wedding dress.

171
00:14:20,460 --> 00:14:21,730
If Mom could have seen this,

172
00:14:22,330 --> 00:14:23,630
She would have said,
"My Jang Mi is so beautiful."

173
00:14:23,970 --> 00:14:26,040
"Jang Mi is my daughter!"

174
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:28,740
She would've been overjoyed.

175
00:14:29,270 --> 00:14:31,410
A wedding that not even my own mother
can attend.

176
00:14:34,510 --> 00:14:35,510
I'm so sorry.

177
00:14:36,210 --> 00:14:38,780
- I'm really so sorry.
- I know. It's okay.

178
00:14:39,750 --> 00:14:41,690
You're doing this to save our family.

179
00:14:43,250 --> 00:14:44,420
I'm the one who should be sorry.

180
00:14:48,030 --> 00:14:50,190
But now that you've made your choice,
I'll be rooting for you.

181
00:14:51,560 --> 00:14:52,560
Be happy.

182
00:15:03,070 --> 00:15:04,540
If I can just get Seo Rin back...

183
00:15:06,110 --> 00:15:08,510
As long as she's safe, I can endure this.

184
00:15:10,110 --> 00:15:11,880
As long as Baek Ho is safe,
that's all I need.

185
00:15:21,130 --> 00:15:22,230
Oh Jang Mi.

186
00:15:26,330 --> 00:15:27,560
Seo Rin.

187
00:15:27,560 --> 00:15:28,670
You backstabber.

188
00:15:32,340 --> 00:15:35,570
We were supposed to switch for one day.
It was just a game!

189
00:15:35,940 --> 00:15:38,510
So how dare someone like you
pretend to be me?

190
00:15:38,880 --> 00:15:41,480
And steal my fiance and my entire life?

191
00:15:41,550 --> 00:15:42,880
I wasn't trying to steal anything,
Seo Rin.

192
00:15:43,450 --> 00:15:47,120
Chae Hwa Young was holding you hostage
and forced me to marry Jun Ho.

193
00:15:47,850 --> 00:15:50,620
Give me a break. What are you, a child?

194
00:15:50,650 --> 00:15:52,320
You're getting married
just because someone told you to?

195
00:15:53,520 --> 00:15:55,360
That's a pathetic excuse, you know?

196
00:15:56,030 --> 00:15:59,530
You wanted to steal my life all along,
didn't you?

197
00:15:59,530 --> 00:16:02,230
That's not it.
Please don't say that, Seo Rin.

198
00:16:02,300 --> 00:16:03,700
"Don't say that?" Give me a break.

199
00:16:03,830 --> 00:16:04,940
Shit.

200
00:16:06,670 --> 00:16:08,810
Now that you've been caught,
you must be terrified, right?

201
00:16:14,780 --> 00:16:16,780
What is this?

202
00:16:16,780 --> 00:16:18,050
What happened to my face?

203
00:16:18,850 --> 00:16:19,850
This can't be happening.

204
00:16:22,490 --> 00:16:25,720
This isn't my face. No!

205
00:16:26,060 --> 00:16:28,890
Seo Rin. It's okay.
Everything's going to be okay.

206
00:16:29,630 --> 00:16:32,530
You did this.
You did this to me, didn't you?

207
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:35,300
Please don't, Seo Rin.
There's someone else behind this.

208
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:37,170
- The person behind this...
- Shut up!

209
00:16:37,500 --> 00:16:38,940
Don't tell me you wanted my life
so badly...

210
00:16:39,200 --> 00:16:41,540
that you tricked me with that nonsense
about switching for a day?

211
00:16:41,540 --> 00:16:43,970
And then you arranged all of this
to get rid of me, right?

212
00:16:44,040 --> 00:16:45,240
Why would I ever try to get rid of you?

213
00:16:45,740 --> 00:16:50,350
We're twins.
We're two halves of the same whole.

214
00:16:50,350 --> 00:16:51,980
So why would I ever want to hurt you?

215
00:16:51,980 --> 00:16:53,550
I'm going through with this wedding,
just to save you,

216
00:16:54,120 --> 00:16:55,890
even though I don't mean it.

217
00:16:55,890 --> 00:16:57,050
Don't be ridiculous.

218
00:16:57,720 --> 00:16:59,960
This is mine. Take it off.

219
00:17:00,020 --> 00:17:02,760
Kang Jun Ho is my man.
Give him back to me!

220
00:17:02,760 --> 00:17:04,060
It's all mine!

221
00:17:18,780 --> 00:17:21,010
What? Did you say Seo Rin is awake?

222
00:17:21,410 --> 00:17:23,010
She's in the bridal suite right now.

223
00:17:23,710 --> 00:17:26,480
Let's go. Make sure no one gets in.

224
00:17:26,780 --> 00:17:27,790
Yes, ma'am.

225
00:17:41,100 --> 00:17:42,100
Seo Rin.

226
00:17:43,170 --> 00:17:45,170
Seo Rin, is it really you?

227
00:17:46,600 --> 00:17:50,840
My daughter, you're awake. Thank goodness.

228
00:17:51,140 --> 00:17:53,340
Ma Seo Rin, don't go to her.

229
00:17:55,480 --> 00:17:56,480
Mom.

230
00:17:57,710 --> 00:17:58,880
Yes, my sweet girl.

231
00:17:59,250 --> 00:18:01,220
Ma Seo Rin, snap out of it.

232
00:18:01,690 --> 00:18:04,620
The one who did that to your face was her,
Chae Hwa Young!

233
00:18:05,090 --> 00:18:07,830
- She tore us apart, stole you away.
- Shut your mouth.

234
00:18:07,830 --> 00:18:10,460
She tried to kill our real mother,
and you almost died because of her.

235
00:18:11,090 --> 00:18:14,830
And you can still call her "Mom?"
Get a grip, Ma Seo Rin!

236
00:18:14,900 --> 00:18:18,170
No, that's not true. It's all lies.
Seo Rin, listen to me.

237
00:18:18,170 --> 00:18:19,840
Oh Jang Mi is the one behind all of this.

238
00:18:20,240 --> 00:18:22,470
She deliberately wore your clothes
and pretended to be you...

239
00:18:22,540 --> 00:18:25,680
so she could stage that whole accident.

240
00:18:25,810 --> 00:18:28,550
And that's how she ruined your face.

241
00:18:28,550 --> 00:18:30,780
Chae Hwa Young,
stop spewing your nonsense.

242
00:18:30,850 --> 00:18:33,350
Oh Jang Mi has always been jealous
of your life.

243
00:18:34,120 --> 00:18:36,420
You're her twin sister,
but you have everything,

244
00:18:37,720 --> 00:18:40,960
while she was dirt poor,
and she was sick with jealousy.

245
00:18:41,360 --> 00:18:44,030
If you were gone,
she could impersonate you...

246
00:18:44,230 --> 00:18:46,500
and take over your entire life.

247
00:18:46,760 --> 00:18:49,570
That's why she tricked all of us
and staged that accident,

248
00:18:50,030 --> 00:18:52,070
so she'd be the only one
to walk away without a scratch.

249
00:18:52,600 --> 00:18:55,210
And in the end, she even stole your man.

250
00:18:55,210 --> 00:18:57,110
Is that really true?

251
00:18:57,170 --> 00:18:58,210
No.

252
00:18:58,440 --> 00:19:01,280
Recall what you knew about Chae Hwa Young
right before your accident.

253
00:19:01,380 --> 00:19:03,880
You know who's lying.
She said she didn't need both of us.

254
00:19:03,950 --> 00:19:05,350
And she tried to kill me.

255
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:08,990
- Don't fall for Chae Hwa Young's lies.
- Shut up, Oh Jang Mi.

256
00:19:09,620 --> 00:19:11,660
Seo Rin,
just look at the situation right now.

257
00:19:12,320 --> 00:19:15,260
Oh Jang Mi is the one
about to marry Kang Jun Ho.

258
00:19:15,460 --> 00:19:17,390
She tried to steal everything from you.

259
00:19:17,390 --> 00:19:19,530
Your love and your man.

260
00:19:19,660 --> 00:19:24,000
Seo Rin, that's not true.
Chae Hwa Young is making all of this up.

261
00:19:24,070 --> 00:19:27,740
Seo Rin, look at her.
Look how vicious she's being.

262
00:19:27,970 --> 00:19:32,380
I tried to stop her from marrying Jun Ho.
He was the man you loved.

263
00:19:32,740 --> 00:19:35,580
I told her no,
but she threatened to tell the Chairman...

264
00:19:35,580 --> 00:19:37,010
and completely forced my hand.

265
00:19:37,450 --> 00:19:39,850
I couldn't let the secret
about you being twins get out,

266
00:19:40,020 --> 00:19:43,420
so I had no choice
but to give in to her blackmail.

267
00:19:43,490 --> 00:19:47,120
Chae Hwa Young, you were the one...

268
00:19:47,620 --> 00:19:49,630
who tried to marry me off
to your son, Kang Jun Ho.

269
00:19:50,090 --> 00:19:53,000
You wanted to get Dream Hotel,
so you held Seo Rin's life hostage.

270
00:19:53,060 --> 00:19:54,870
- Oh Jang Mi.
- Wait, Jun Ho...

271
00:19:55,730 --> 00:19:57,070
is your son?

272
00:20:12,750 --> 00:20:16,490
What is she talking about?
What did she just say about Jun Ho?

273
00:20:17,590 --> 00:20:18,690
Cut the nonsense.

274
00:20:19,360 --> 00:20:20,890
Enough with the lies.

275
00:20:22,060 --> 00:20:23,560
Are you really going to deny your own son?

276
00:20:25,360 --> 00:20:26,830
Don't pay any attention to her, Seo Rin.

277
00:20:27,600 --> 00:20:31,540
Look at her.
She's desperate and spouting nonsense.

278
00:20:31,800 --> 00:20:32,900
Why wouldn't she be?

279
00:20:33,070 --> 00:20:37,410
She's going back to her side-dish shop,
so she's lying through her teeth.

280
00:20:37,470 --> 00:20:38,540
That's not true, Seo Rin.

281
00:20:38,940 --> 00:20:41,580
Don't let Chae Hwa Young fool you.
It's all lies.

282
00:20:42,410 --> 00:20:45,580
Get out of the way.
Seo Rin needs to go back to the hospital.

283
00:20:46,680 --> 00:20:49,350
Seo Rin, now that you're awake,

284
00:20:49,850 --> 00:20:53,160
Mom will get you plastic surgery
to make you look like your old self again.

285
00:20:54,290 --> 00:20:57,260
And as for Oh Jang Mi,
we'll send her back to where she belongs.

286
00:20:57,590 --> 00:21:02,470
Mom, the surgery can make me
look like I used to, right?

287
00:21:03,130 --> 00:21:05,040
Will I be able to see Jun Ho again?

288
00:21:05,340 --> 00:21:07,500
Of course. Let's go.

289
00:21:08,610 --> 00:21:13,140
Don't go with Chae Hwa Young, Seo Rin.
You'll just go back to your old life.

290
00:21:13,410 --> 00:21:17,180
- You'll be trapped by her all over again!
- Move! I said get out of the way!

291
00:21:18,350 --> 00:21:20,450
Get off her, you leech!

292
00:21:21,720 --> 00:21:26,120
Your little show is over now.
You're done pretending to be Seo Rin.

293
00:21:26,320 --> 00:21:28,160
Now go back to where you belong.

294
00:21:33,600 --> 00:21:34,600
Seo Rin!

295
00:21:39,070 --> 00:21:40,070
Seo Rin.

296
00:21:41,240 --> 00:21:42,310
Seo Rin, no!

297
00:21:42,810 --> 00:21:43,810
Seo Rin.

298
00:21:44,110 --> 00:21:46,980
Seo Rin, please. Don't go.

299
00:21:47,410 --> 00:21:49,280
Don't go. Seo Rin, please.

300
00:21:49,280 --> 00:21:50,380
Seo Rin!

301
00:21:55,390 --> 00:21:56,390
Where is she?

302
00:21:58,560 --> 00:21:59,560
Jang Mi.

303
00:22:00,620 --> 00:22:02,660
- Here.
- Baek Ho!

304
00:22:03,960 --> 00:22:07,460
- What am I going to do about Seo Rin?
- What happened to her?

305
00:22:08,100 --> 00:22:09,970
Did Chae Hwa Young take Seo Rin with her?

306
00:22:10,670 --> 00:22:14,040
I couldn't stop her.
What's going to happen to Seo Rin?

307
00:22:14,870 --> 00:22:17,940
I'll save Seo Rin no matter what,
so don't you worry.

308
00:22:22,150 --> 00:22:23,150
It's okay.

309
00:22:23,910 --> 00:22:25,320
Everything's going to be okay now.

310
00:22:29,520 --> 00:22:32,460
Wait, who did this to you?
Did CEO Chae do this to you?

311
00:22:33,060 --> 00:22:36,060
Why did you just stand there and take it?
You should've hit her back.

312
00:22:38,100 --> 00:22:39,100
Let's go.

313
00:23:00,420 --> 00:23:02,520
Mom, why are you calling
instead of coming here?

314
00:23:03,690 --> 00:23:07,420
Hong Ju, Seo Rin is back.

315
00:23:07,490 --> 00:23:11,700
What? What are you talking about?
Seo Rin's in the bridal suite right now.

316
00:23:11,760 --> 00:23:15,030
No, the one in the bridal suite
is Oh Jang Mi.

317
00:23:15,430 --> 00:23:19,840
Seo Rin came back with a scar on her face.

318
00:23:19,900 --> 00:23:22,610
What? Then what's going to happen
to the wedding?

319
00:23:22,940 --> 00:23:24,980
- Is it off?
- What are you talking about?

320
00:23:41,960 --> 00:23:42,960
Jun Ho!

321
00:23:44,590 --> 00:23:47,600
Don't tell me Baek Ho just ran off
with Oh Jang Mi.

322
00:23:51,870 --> 00:23:52,870
Jang Mi.

323
00:24:00,540 --> 00:24:02,110
I'm sorry, Jun Ho.

324
00:24:02,910 --> 00:24:03,910
Don't go.

325
00:24:05,120 --> 00:24:08,190
I can't give up on Baek Ho.

326
00:24:09,320 --> 00:24:10,320
Get in, Jang Mi.

327
00:24:18,630 --> 00:24:19,630
Are you ready?

328
00:24:20,500 --> 00:24:21,970
Yes, let's go.

329
00:24:51,030 --> 00:24:52,030
Seo Rin.

330
00:24:52,560 --> 00:24:56,370
Actually, your grandfather's health
isn't very good.

331
00:24:57,170 --> 00:24:59,240
He almost collapsed not too long ago,

332
00:24:59,670 --> 00:25:03,210
- so he can't handle any major shocks.
- Grandpa is sick?

333
00:25:03,570 --> 00:25:04,740
How sick is he?

334
00:25:05,980 --> 00:25:08,450
He's under care now, so he'll get better.

335
00:25:09,280 --> 00:25:10,750
So, Seo Rin...

336
00:25:11,280 --> 00:25:14,920
Let's have you stay here
until your surgery, okay?

337
00:25:15,120 --> 00:25:17,220
You mean I can't go back to my own house?
That's insane.

338
00:25:17,550 --> 00:25:21,360
Shit. So you'll just let Oh Jang Mi
keep pretending to be me until then?

339
00:25:21,630 --> 00:25:23,660
We don't have a choice right now, do we?

340
00:25:24,900 --> 00:25:25,900
This is so frustrating!

341
00:25:26,700 --> 00:25:29,130
Pack up my clothes and my things
and bring them to me.

342
00:25:29,400 --> 00:25:31,030
And hurry up
and schedule the plastic surgery.

343
00:25:33,000 --> 00:25:35,370
Of course. I'll do it right away.

344
00:25:36,140 --> 00:25:38,340
My sweet girl!

345
00:25:39,410 --> 00:25:43,210
You have no idea how happy it makes me
to see you awake.

346
00:25:44,050 --> 00:25:46,220
And I won't have to be blackmailed
by Oh Jang Mi anymore.

347
00:25:47,620 --> 00:25:48,650
But, Mom.

348
00:25:50,020 --> 00:25:52,960
Is it true that
you don't need two of us...

349
00:25:53,220 --> 00:25:55,260
that you're planning on killing one of us?

350
00:25:56,430 --> 00:25:59,300
Seo Rin, ever since you started
hanging out with Oh Jang Mi,

351
00:25:59,960 --> 00:26:02,130
you were being gaslit by her, weren't you?

352
00:26:02,770 --> 00:26:05,000
She was so blinded by jealousy
when she saw you,

353
00:26:05,100 --> 00:26:07,100
so everything she says is a lie.

354
00:26:07,970 --> 00:26:09,570
She's your twin sister,
but I can't believe...

355
00:26:09,570 --> 00:26:10,610
how different you two are.

356
00:26:11,470 --> 00:26:13,710
I guess that's what growing up poor
does to a person.

357
00:26:14,410 --> 00:26:16,780
But you're the one who's lying.

358
00:26:16,780 --> 00:26:18,520
And to think Kang Jun Ho is your son.

359
00:26:24,290 --> 00:26:25,290
Ma'am.

360
00:26:35,000 --> 00:26:36,230
The Chairman is asking for you.

361
00:26:38,570 --> 00:26:39,840
The wedding's been called off, right?

362
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:42,310
All the guests have been led to believe
that the wedding has been canceled...

363
00:26:42,510 --> 00:26:45,740
since Seo Rin collapsed
and was rushed to the hospital.

364
00:26:45,940 --> 00:26:47,010
What did the Chairman say?

365
00:26:47,710 --> 00:26:51,480
I'm worried that old man will raise a fuss
about coming here to see Seo Rin.

366
00:26:51,580 --> 00:26:54,820
I told him she needs absolute rest,
so no visitors are allowed.

367
00:26:55,890 --> 00:26:58,120
I'm going to see the Chairman first.

368
00:26:58,120 --> 00:26:59,620
You keep a close eye on Seo Rin.

369
00:27:00,020 --> 00:27:01,830
Yes. Be careful.

370
00:27:19,040 --> 00:27:20,210
Keep an eye on me?

371
00:27:20,810 --> 00:27:23,510
Shit. Do you think
I'll let you get your way?

372
00:27:24,450 --> 00:27:26,250
I'll give you some time for now.

373
00:27:26,920 --> 00:27:30,290
But you will pay dearly
for the crimes you've committed.

374
00:27:32,020 --> 00:27:33,820
(Suk Hee's Side Dishes)

375
00:27:36,390 --> 00:27:38,060
You're so pretty, Jang Mi.

376
00:27:38,700 --> 00:27:40,500
My wonderful Jang Mi.

377
00:27:41,530 --> 00:27:43,600
Jang Mi is Suk Hee's daughter.

378
00:27:44,900 --> 00:27:46,740
My Jang Mi is so pretty.

379
00:27:49,210 --> 00:27:51,270
I love how you smell, Mom.

380
00:27:58,750 --> 00:28:02,520
Running off with the bride and everything.
I'm impressed, Kang Baek Ho.

381
00:28:03,090 --> 00:28:04,090
Come on.

382
00:28:39,860 --> 00:28:41,520
(The First Man)

383
00:28:41,590 --> 00:28:45,430
I chose you, Jun Ho,
because I was in love with Baek Ho.

384
00:28:45,700 --> 00:28:48,600
So please, just move on, Jun Ho.

385
00:28:48,830 --> 00:28:51,370
Any news on Seo Rin?
Did you check the side dish shop?

386
00:28:51,470 --> 00:28:54,540
- She's not there.
- Then where in the world did she go?

387
00:28:54,800 --> 00:28:57,910
Grandpa, I have someone for you to meet.

388
00:28:58,140 --> 00:29:00,410
What in the world is going on?

389
00:29:00,880 --> 00:29:02,810
We're twins.

390
00:29:04,850 --> 00:29:06,850
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
